en_353828_0	An awareness workshop to stimulate the value of cultivation and educate the troops on the importance of growing own vegetables, fruits, flowers, herbal plants, rare creepers, etc was held for troops under command to Divisions, Brigades, Battalions and Training schools of the Security Forces Headquarters Jaffna during 6-7 November at the SFHQ-J auditorium.
en_353828_1	This programme was conducted on the guidelines given by the Commander of the Army Lieutenant General Shavendra Silva and with the blessings of the Jaffna Commander.
en_353828_2	Officers from the Directorate of Agriculture and Livestock conducted lectures and practicals related to gardening and garden beautification.
